  "Examinable courses leading either to a post-secondary qualification (below degree) or recognised under a Singapore Government agency's regulatory or professional development framework for the sector.": "可考核的課程，可獲得中學後資格（低於學位），或在新加坡政府機構針對該行業的監管或專業發展框架下獲得認可。",
