  "We sit with you to understand the learner, the sector and the standard. From this we draw a single competency map that holds the rest of the programme together.": "我們與您共同探討，理解學員、行業與標準。在此基礎上，我們繪製一張統一的能力圖譜，將整個課程的其餘部分串聯起來。",
