  "We draft the Course Proposal (CP) Form, lesson and assessment plans, trainer guide and learner materials, all version-controlled and submission-ready.": "我們擬寫課程提案（CP）表格、課程與評估計劃、培訓師指南及學員材料，全部進行版本控制並可隨時提交。",
