  "Both our in-house creative producer and PixPlaySG deliver online and offline graphic work, from banners, flyers and posters to social media posts.": "我們的內部創意製作人與 PixPlaySG 雙方皆能交付線上線下的平面作品，從橫幅、傳單與海報到社交媒體貼文。",
  "A training provider is judged on its prospectus and remembered for its delivery. We work on the delivery, quietly, so the prospectus is never a promise the practice cannot keep.": "培訓機構因其招生簡章而受評判，因其交付而被銘記。我們默默致力於交付，使招生簡章永不成為機構無法兌現的承諾。",
