  "The shape of correspondence, monochrome study, the solidity of a working practice.": "來函往來的形態，單色研究，一所運作中事務所的堅實。",
  "Tell us a little about your sector and the courses you train. We will be in touch about adding you to the community.": "請簡略告訴我們您所屬的領域以及您所授的課程。我們將就將您納入社群一事與您聯繫。",
  "Tell us about your domain and where you have practised. We will write back about engagements we are working on that may fit your standing.": "請告訴我們您的專業領域以及您曾執業之處。我們將就手上可能契合您資歷的委託回信予您。",
