  "2birds": "2birds",
  "Keith Ho": "Keith Ho",
  "Founder · Curriculum Developer In House Legal Counsel": "創辦人 · 課程開發者 內部法律顧問",
  "Bachelor of Laws (Hons) (UK) SDip (HRM), MSHRI DACE, ACLP, ACTA, IAL-SAE TAEPP Level 3 Senior Professional AE HRD Corp Accredited Trainer (Msia) Verify TAEPP ↗": "法學學士（榮譽）（英國） SDip (HRM), MSHRI DACE, ACLP, ACTA, IAL-SAE TAEPP 第三級高級專業 AE HRD Corp 認證培訓師（馬來西亞） 驗證 TAEPP ↗",
  "keith.ho@2birds.asia": "keith.ho@2birds.asia",
  "Keith Ho is a training and education professional with more than a decade in the Training and Adult Education sector. He serves as General Manager of 1ST Aid and Healthcare Pte. Ltd. and runs 2birds, an independent advisory and course development practice.": "Keith Ho 是一位培訓與教育專才，在培訓及成人教育領域擁有逾十年經驗。他擔任 1ST Aid and Healthcare Pte. Ltd. 的總經理，並經營 2birds——一所獨立的諮詢及課程開發事務所。",
  "He holds a Bachelor of Laws (Hons) from Birmingham City University, an Allied Certificate in Legal Skills from Temasek Polytechnic, a Specialist Diploma in Human Resource Management from Nanyang Polytechnic, a Diploma in Adult and Continuing Education (DACE) and an Advanced Certificate in Training and Assessment (ACTA) from the Institute for Adult Learning. He is a recognised IAL Specialist Adult Educator, a member of the Singapore Human Resources Institute (MSHRI) and a HRD Corp certified trainer in Malaysia.": "他持有 Birmingham City University 的法學學士（榮譽）學位、Temasek Polytechnic 的法律技能輔修證書、Nanyang Polytechnic 的人力資源管理專科文憑，以及 Institute for Adult Learning 頒授的成人及持續教育文憑（DACE）和培訓與評估高級證書（ACTA）。他是經認可的 IAL 專業成人教育工作者、新加坡人力資源學院會員（MSHRI），以及馬來西亞的 HRD Corp 認證培訓師。",
  "His career has spanned the Singapore Productivity Centre, the Institute of Singapore Chartered Accountants and Adept Academy. At SGPC, he developed courses including the Fair Tenancy Industry Committee programme, which The Business Times featured in 2022 for promoting the Fair Tenancy Code of Conduct between landlords and tenants. At Adept Academy, he contributed to curriculum development and training innovation and achieved a Grade 1 outcome under SSG's Training Provider Quality Assurance framework. In 2025, SSG invited him as a speaker to share best practices with the training provider community.": "他的職業生涯橫跨 Singapore Productivity Centre、Institute of Singapore Chartered Accountants 及 Adept Academy。在 SGPC，他開發了多門課程，包括 Fair Tenancy Industry Committee 項目，該項目因推廣業主與租戶之間的 Fair Tenancy Code of Conduct，於 2022 年獲 The Business Times 專題報導。在 Adept Academy，他參與課程開發與培訓創新，並在 SSG 的培訓機構質量保證框架下取得第一級（Grade 1）成績。2025 年，SSG 邀請他作為講者，向培訓機構社群分享最佳實踐。",
  "He works within SSG frameworks including WSQ and CASL, and has facilitated training delivery and courseware development for the Singapore Furniture Industries Council Institute, Xprienz, Carrie Academy International, Focus Learning Centre, QD Academy, Addison Institute and HY M&E Consultancy, covering artificial intelligence, healthcare, human resources, legal, leadership, food safety, built environment, data science, supply chain and digital analytics.": "他在 SSG 框架（包括 WSQ 與 CASL）下開展工作，並曾為 Singapore Furniture Industries Council Institute、Xprienz、Carrie Academy International、Focus Learning Centre、QD Academy、Addison Institute 及 HY M&E Consultancy 提供培訓實施與課程開發支援，涵蓋人工智能、醫療保健、人力資源、法律、領導力、食品安全、建築環境、數據科學、供應鏈及數位分析等領域。",
  "Correspondence with Keith is welcome by email at keith.ho@2birds.asia.": "歡迎透過電子郵件 keith.ho@2birds.asia 與 Keith 聯繫。",
