  "Write to us, and we will write back.": "來信予我們，我們必將回覆。",
  "If you are a certified adult educator or a subject matter expert with standing in your sector, leave us a short note. We read every submission and reply within five working days. There is no fee, no obligation, and no exclusivity.": "若您是經認證的成人教育工作者，或在所屬行業中享有聲望的領域專家，請給我們留下簡短的訊息。我們會閱讀每一份提交，並在五個工作日內回覆。無須費用，無任何義務，亦無排他性。",
  "I. All information is held in confidence and used only to assess fit.": "I. 所有資訊均予以保密，僅用於評估匹配度。",
  "II. Joining the community is by invitation; submission is not acceptance.": "II. 加入社群須經邀請；提交並不等同於獲接納。",
  "III. We are equally glad to hear from practitioners outside this list of sectors.": "III. 我們同樣樂於聽到來自此行業清單之外的從業者來信。",
