  "Submit application": "提交申請",
  "By submitting, you consent to 2birds contacting you in respect of this application.": "提交即表示您同意 2birds 就本申請與您聯絡。",
  "Trainers and SMEs Sourcing": "培訓師與 SME 尋聘",
  "A community of practitioners, on call.": "一支隨時待命的從業者社群。",
  "The toughest part of most curriculum development is finding the subject-matter expert. We keep a working community of practitioners across the sectors in which we currently practise, pair them to the engagement at no cost to the training provider, and warmly invite trainers and subject-matter experts in other sectors to work with us.": "大多數課程開發中最棘手的部分，是找到合適的領域專家。我們在目前從事實踐的各行業中維持著一支務實的從業者社群，將他們與項目配對而不向培訓機構收取任何費用，並誠摯邀請其他行業的培訓師與領域專家與我們合作。",
  "An arch holds quietly because every stone is set in its right place. A community of practitioners works the same way, matched to the engagement, no more, no less.": "拱門得以靜靜屹立，是因為每一塊石頭都安放在正確的位置。從業者社群亦是如此運作——與項目恰當配對，不多，亦不少。",
  "The shape of a community · still life · restraint as a working principle.": "社群的形態 · 靜物 · 以克制為行事之本。",
  "SSG's Skills Demand for the Future Economy report organises Singapore's sectoral demand around three priority economies. Our community currently practises within parts of each, and grows by invitation rather than by overreach.": "SSG 的《未來經濟技能需求》報告將新加坡的行業需求歸納為三大優先經濟。我們的社群目前在其中各部分從事實踐，並以邀請而非過度擴張的方式成長。",
  "Curriculum rarely fails for want of a writer. It fails for want of the one person who has actually done the work, and finding that person is the real engagement.": "課程鮮少因缺少撰寫者而失敗，而是因缺少那位真正做過這項工作的人而失敗——找到那個人，才是真正的工程。",
  "From the practice · Sourcing": "源自本所實踐 · 尋聘",
  "In demand courses": "熱門需求課程",
  "§ III · The pairing": "§ III · 配對",
  "Paired to your engagement, at no cost to you, and none to the learner.": "與您的項目配對，您無須付費，學員亦無須付費。",
  "The toughest part of most curriculum development is the subject-matter expert. Without one, the Course Proposal Form cannot be submitted; with the wrong one, the courseware will not survive the Course Quality Check. We keep a working community, prepared and ready, drawn from practitioners who have committed time to the community on the same understanding that we have: that good training ought not to be priced out of reach.": "大多數課程開發中最棘手的部分，便是領域專家。沒有領域專家，《課程建議書》便無法提交；找錯了人，課程教材則無法通過課程質量檢查。我們維持著一支務實、隨時待命的社群，成員來自那些以與我們相同的理念投入時間於社群的從業者：好的培訓不應被定價至遙不可及。",
  "Where your engagement can be matched from our community, the pairing is free. We do not levy a finder's fee, a placement margin or a per-hour markup on top of the SME's own rate. Where our practitioners cannot match the engagement, we source through the usual recruitment channels (Jobstreet and the like) and recover only the direct costs of the search and administrative costs.": "凡您的項目能從我們社群中匹配時，配對均為免費。我們不會在 SME 自身費率之上加收介紹費、安置差價或按小時的加價。若我們的從業者無法匹配該項目，我們將透過常規招聘渠道（如 Jobstreet 等）尋聘，並僅收回搜尋的直接成本與行政成本。",
  "A short note on what we are not: 2birds is not a recruitment agency. We do not hold a recruitment licence and we do not place candidates into employment. We make introductions; we do not negotiate contracts on anyone's behalf.": "關於我們並非什麼，謹作簡短說明：2birds 並非招聘仲介。我們不持有招聘牌照，也不為候選人安排就業。我們只作引薦；我們不代表任何一方協商合約。",
  "An invitation": "一份邀請",
  "If you are a certified adult educator or a subject-matter expert with standing in your sector, write to us. Our community is open by invitation, and we are always glad to be in correspondence with practitioners we have not yet met.": "若您是經認證的成人教育工作者，或在所屬行業中享有聲望的領域專家，請來信予我們。我們的社群以邀請方式開放，而我們始終樂於與尚未謀面的從業者書信往來。",
  "– A standing invitation to the practice": "— 一份對本所敞開的長期邀請",
