  "Replies within two working days, during business hours.": "於辦公時間內兩個工作天內回覆。",
  "Monday to Friday09:00am to 06:00pm": "星期一至星期五　上午 9:00 至下午 6:00",
  "Excluding weekends and public holidays.": "週末及公眾假期除外。",
  "The consultation is ours to offer, with no obligation. You will hear from us within two working days.":
    "此次諮詢由本所免費提供，並無任何義務。您將於兩個工作天內收到我們的回覆。",
  "Open": "可預約",
