  /* ---- contact page ---- */
  "We would be glad to hear from you. Whether you are a training provider weighing an engagement, a trainer or SME considering joining us, or simply curious, a note is always welcome. You will hear from us within two working days.":
    "我們很樂意收到您的來函。無論您是正在考慮委託的培訓機構、有意加入我們的培訓師或領域專家，抑或只是單純感興趣，我們都歡迎您的留言。您將於兩個工作天內收到回覆。",
  "A working metaphor": "一則貼切的隱喻",
  "Correspondence with the practice is a quiet thing, the work behind it solid. Write to us and we will write back.":
    "與本所的往來是一件低調的事，而其背後的工作則堅實可靠。來函予我們，我們必復函予您。",
  "§ I · The form": "§ I · 表格",
  "Tell us, in your own words, what the engagement looks like. We will reply within two working days during Singapore business hours.":
    "請用您自己的話告訴我們，這項委託大致是怎樣的。我們將於新加坡辦公時間內兩個工作天內回覆。",
  "I am writing as": "我的身分是",
